subject: Little League World Series
Baseball
Little League
lead_paragraph: Levi Rudolph pitched four-plus innings and drove home a run with a bunt single as Lake Oswego, Ore., defeated Hamilton, Ohio, 6-1, Tuesday to advance to the Little League World Series semifinals.
